sentences.english: The period of effectiveness an authorizing contract may not exceed 10 years.
sentences.chinese: 許可合同的有效期限一次不得超過十年。

sentences.english: Travel days may be used consecutively or non-consecutively within the validity period.
sentences.chinese: 在有效期內可乘車日可以是連續或非連續使用。

sentences.english: Conclusion This eye drops may be stored for 4 months at room temperature.
sentences.chinese: 結論地塞米松氯黴素滴眼液的有效期暫定爲4個月。

sentences.english: UK visa only valid 30 days, Schengen visa for 90 days.
sentences.chinese: 英國簽證有效期僅爲30天，申根國家爲90天。

sentences.english: Article 51. Normative documents shall be valid for five years.
sentences.chinese: 第五十一條規範性文件有效期爲5年。

sentences.english: It shall be valid for an indefinite time period until its termination by DFTT with notice.
sentences.chinese: 它的有效期直至DFTT公司通知客戶終止協議爲止。

sentences.english: Out insurance covers only W. P. A. including warehouse to warehouse clause valid for 15 days.
sentences.chinese: 我們只保水漬險，包括倉對倉條款有效期十五天。

sentences.english: These are the conditions under which the expiration date shall apply.
sentences.chinese: 在有效期內，藥品應在規定的各條件下貯存。

sentences.english: Article 23 The certificate of Chinese name-brand product shall be valid for three years.
sentences.chinese: 第二十三條中國名牌產品證書的有效期爲三年。

sentences.english: E. The people who hold the card must pay commission charge before period of validity.
sentences.chinese: 持卡者須在有效期前到俱樂部交納相應手續費。

sentences.english: How long is the boat time table effective?
sentences.chinese: 行船時刻表有效期是多長時間？

sentences.english: The probationary period shall be included in the term of this Contract.
sentences.chinese: 試用期被包括在本合同的有效期限內。

sentences.english: By the research of the stability of HYBR-003 pharmaceutics, the validity of HYBR-003 pharmaceutics also has been determined.
sentences.chinese: 通過對製劑的穩定性研究，確定了製劑的有效期。

sentences.english: I ask Congress to renew it.
sentences.chinese: 我要求國會延長這一權力的有效期限。
